      "weather": "FINE",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIJINKERY (2) is a well performed dog and winner of eight races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at Angle Park (30.85). Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Rates on top in this line up. HERE COMES RHEA (1) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by a neck at Murray Bridge Straight in a handy 19.84. Well suited by the inside box and likes the trip. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Deserves serious consideration again. TENACIOUS DESIGN (8) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at Murray Bridge in a handy 22.56 beating Compton Stella. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. MYAH MISS (4) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
